e home page click the &quot;Create Event&quot; button. Then fill in a sensible name, description and location for the event. &#10;Then select the date of the event from the drop down calendar. Then enter the time start and end, and toggle the button &#10;for AM/PM. Then enter a number for the number of volunteers this event needs. Finally click the &quot;Create Event&quot; button&#10;and the event will be added to the events list. &#10;&#10;Delete Event (Feature available for: Admin): &#10;From the home page click on the &quot;Admins&quot; button. Then click on the &quot;Events&quot; tab in the top left of the screen. From here&#10;select the event you want to delete from the event list on the left side under the &quot;Events&quot; tab. Then click on the &quot;Cancel &#10;Event&quot; button to cancle the event.&#10;&#10;Delete User (Feature available for: Admin):&#10;From the home page click on the &quot;Admins&quot; button. Then select the user you are trying to delete from the list on the left&#10;under the &quot;Volunteers&quot; tab. Then in order to delete the user from the system click the &quot;Delete&quot; button on the bottom.&#10;&#10;Run User Report (Feature available for: Admin): &#10;From the home page click on the &quot;Admins&quot; button.  hen select the user you are trying to run a report on from the list on &#10;the left under the &quot;Volunteers&quot; tab. Then click on the &quot;Run Employee Summary Report&quot; button to run the report. The data&#10;from the report will then be displayed on the screen.">
